    "description": "感谢您体验《高考之路》Demo版，请您花几分钟时间完成一下新品节的问卷，以便我们更好地优化游戏内容。<br>问卷传送门：<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >背景故事</h2>20XX年,由不秃头科技研发的模拟器正式上市，该款产品可在一天之内模拟考生一百天的考试规划，从而帮助考生提升成绩。<br>玩家将扮演一名刚收到模拟器的考生，在模拟器中不断打磨自己的备(da)考(pai)方(ji)案(shu)<br>距离高考开始只有一百天，你将怎样安排自己的每一天呢？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/feee4a3a6560e92ff1883b11fc9f7e2f.avif?t=1693206347\" width=550 height=79 /></span><br>作为勤奋的高三学生，玩家在学习时，将会遇到例如蕉绿、马虎、寒树之类众多由困难具象成的敌人，战胜他们才能获得知识和更多卡牌。玩家需要升级和构筑你的牌组，策略性地组合搭配卡牌打出最佳的效果，挑战三模、二模和最终的高考之战！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/f6ef9a83579cd07b691a5693002f01b3.poster.avif?t=1693206347\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/f6ef9a83579cd07b691a5693002f01b3.webm?t=1693206347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/f6ef9a83579cd07b691a5693002f01b3.mp4?t=1693206347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/c370063392f53047d3b042864f6da325.avif?t=1693206347\" width=550 height=79 /></span><br>高考倒计时100天期间，在这个游戏中的小镇感受高中生活的乐趣。玩家可以自由前往地图中的各个区域，吃喝玩乐或是勤学苦练，分配自己的时间和体力、金钱，穿梭于在图书馆、家、食堂等地，做足准备迎接即将到来的高考。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/df07e724de63b976fa3a4f05aa3950be.poster.avif?t=1693206347\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/df07e724de63b976fa3a4f05aa3950be.webm?t=1693206347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/df07e724de63b976fa3a4f05aa3950be.mp4?t=1693206347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/3d7fee3c017d5d185fb063fa5d4eb651.avif?t=1693206347\" width=550 height=79 /></span><br>前往小镇上任意地点做事都需要耗费固定的时间，所以需要自行规划好自己的衣食住行，要注意睡眠时间，不合理的规划将影响主角的身心状态哦~当然，也可以用滑板、自行车等代步工具来提升走路的速度。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/fe7032d87a83ebb5ac5f216bc89e9081.poster.avif?t=1693206347\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/fe7032d87a83ebb5ac5f216bc89e9081.webm?t=1693206347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/fe7032d87a83ebb5ac5f216bc89e9081.mp4?t=1693206347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/1fc3ad0054b3977328633168196c3c91.avif?t=1693206347\" width=550 height=79 /></span><br>高中生活不止有学习，还要吃吃喝喝锻炼身体！玩家需要操纵主角在食堂或是购买小卖部的零食填充饱食度（食堂更便宜，但是零食可以随身携带！），在操场参加拔河、跑步等运动可以增加体能，告别疲惫，成为健康的学霸。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/72a3a55d558170ea4c5ad0fa9660d013.poster.avif?t=1693206347\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/72a3a55d558170ea4c5ad0fa9660d013.webm?t=1693206347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/72a3a55d558170ea4c5ad0fa9660d013.mp4?t=1693206347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/bccde9c54d4147a5e264ee15042c918c.avif?t=1693206347\" width=550 height=79 /></span><br>适当的劳逸结合很有必要哦！长时间的学习和奔波可能导致心情低落，玩家可以在网吧中玩一些小游戏来使自己心情变好，还能感受一下网吧的泡面和烤肠等经典小吃，告别饥饿。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/cb2225df19d3e93ff0ddc1a23bc0ba68.poster.avif?t=1693206347\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/cb2225df19d3e93ff0ddc1a23bc0ba68.webm?t=1693206347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/cb2225df19d3e93ff0ddc1a23bc0ba68.mp4?t=1693206347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>目前开发团队只有2人，除了开发，还要接一些项目维持日常花销，所以项目开发可能还需要一段时间，感谢大家的支持和等待！<br>欢迎大家加入《高考之路》官方玩家群：720493479",
